source.37636c01:
The authors of Fast.ai recommend using the values from the learning rate finder in one of two ways:

1. Take the minimum learning rate and then divide it by 10.
2. Use the learning rate from the steepest point on the graph.

Both of these are given automatically by the `lr_find` method.
source.59832e16:
# About competition

Using 6000 training data /food images/ to build a deep learning - food classifier model. Predicting 4000 test data images with best possible accuracy.

#### About data
Images are all ".jpg"
- train - training data /6000 images/
- test - testing data /4000 images/
- submission.csv - Submission template
- training.csv - Training data with labels
- category.csv - Definition of food classification types



Column dictionary
- filename - Image index name
- category_id - Food types /numbers/
- category_name - Food types' definition /food names/
